	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The boxes were using fixed sizes measured in <strong>px</strong>, while you had your computer's fonts set larger than expected. I changed them to fixed sizes measured in <strong>em</strong> to adapt better to font size.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


